strings: <se_low>Boiler: Now stand in front of your crystal ball and focus on what is bothering you.
<se_low>Boiler: Yes, that's right, the fog is getting thicker. I see the castle!
<se_low>Boiler: I see kings and queens who smile at what you seek.
<se_low>Boiler: All I can say is this. The rest is up to you.
